name: Territorial Sharpjaw
text:
Flood {3}{g}{g} (During your turn, you may pay {3}{g}{g} and exile this card from your hand flooding target land. It loses all land types and abilities, and it gains “{T}: Add {1}.”)

Whenever you flood Territorial Sharpjaw or it dies, create X 1/1 green Fish creature tokens, where X is Territorial Sharpjaw’s power.
